des:
It's been more than a decade since we were introduced to the Marvel Cinematic Universe and we still can't get enough of our favorite superheroes. Wherever we go, we see them. This unofficial Marvel Trivia is a perfect quiz to test if we can best your Marvel knowledge.
Say "open Unofficial Marvel Trivia" to start the quiz and enjoy. 
So do you have what it takes to be worthy? Either way, we love you 3000!
